{"tid":1429560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[家庭文宣]如何回應民意逆轉觀點","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:51:10.000Z","uid":57911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"864e1c7cda86f739359e91b9b76632525220803b","tid":1429560,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:00:51.000Z","msg":"真實故事<br />\n老竇好關心前線年輕人<br />\n驚前線受傷<br />\n驚前線俾差人拉<br />\n驚前線坐監前途盡毀<br />\n覺得唔值得對個咁嘅政權付出咁嘅代價<br />\n成日叫我出post勸退前線啲手足<br />\n叫你哋走得嘅走唔好俾人拉<br />\n留力等十月一先出嚟全民慶祝國慶<br />\n老竇話日日咁搞唔係辦法<br />\n話會令民意逆轉<br />\n<br />\n我答佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">其實宜家得兩個立場</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 撐唔撐成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n2. 同情前線手足多啲定同情差佬多啲</span><br />\n<br />\n老竇聽完冇聲出<br />\n我再補多一句<br />\n其實林病肯<span style=\"color: red;\">講撤回</span><br />\n並<span style=\"color: red;\">馬上成立獨立調查委員會</span><br />\n其實<span style=\"color: orange;\">啲人就會散</span><br />\n<br />\n老竇反問我咁之前犧牲咗啲人點？<br />\n就咁算？<br />\n我答佢係<br />\n有獨立調查委員會會查<br />\n<br />\n就咁樣，老竇靜咗一晚"},{"pid":"a760dafb807fe2ff3e130c97083ceef3b780bbaf","tid":1429560,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"深信自推十連會有巴打幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441197f31e890a256a0faeb403a1b79e97029a35","tid":1429560,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:04:47.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"92518938cba3b448d9a5043780d90402285d5fc3","tid":1429560,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"82d6cccbd13591f5b57e476cd00aa4c3f67e2da5","tid":1429560,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"587dc71e5274b72761efae3cddcf6d70329b19ba","tid":1429560,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5f7cf7d2e828232bc828b2a81c518dc5d81181b1","tid":1429560,